                    <span>This audio program helped me take one of the most difficult experiences I've gone through in a long time and turn it into a pathway to healing. I was continually amazed and inspired by the material, the exercises, and Debbie's loving presence. I used the program at a time when I was experiencing some depression and found that it not only helped me shift out of that, but it helped me make peace with my past and get inspired about my future.  The best $30 you could possibly spend.  Buy it, make the time for it, and do it.</span>
                  
